			  			I currently see a lot of confusion about scripts.<br />
<br />
Since SSL is gone it's possible to use scripts again, however most script packages link to the old adress and aren't working.<br />
Moreover, some players are unsure if scripts are allowed, some scripts are public, some are secret, a lot of players doesn't even know about scripts seemingly.<br />
<br />
In case you don't know, there are automated scripts for making fleets, sort commanders (not only viewing), analyse battle reports, mass-messaging, auto-blockade, different IRC combined scripts etc.<br />
<br />
Personally, I like scripts but without doubt there is an unfair advantage over players that don't use them resp. don't know about them. <br><p>-----------------------------------<br />
